## ğŸ§  Objectives
- Make CNC/programming education **inclusive** for blind and low-vision students  
- Provide a **modular educational kit** with Braille-based blocks and open documentation  
- Support teachers with ready-to-use **lesson plans, CAD files, and STL models**

